    "date": "2005-09-16T19:02:44Z",
    "text": "Amends the Internal Revenue Code to revise mortgage revenue bond rules for the financing of home improvement loans for residences in disaster areas. Increases the limitation on such loans from $15,000 to $150,000. Waives certain income requirements for such loans and the three-year replacement requirement for residences destroyed in a disaster."
